    "mice.service2.description": "Premier platforms that unite the global healthcare community. Gervae provides comprehensive operational management for leading medical exhibitions and symposia, showcasing the latest advances in healthcare technology, medical equipment, and clinical innovation.",
    "mice.service3.title": "Medical Associations Conferences",
    "mice.service3.description": "Gervae offers dedicated, end-to-end event management for professional medical unions and scientific societies. From scientific programme coordination to delegate hospitality, we ensure annual conferences meet the highest standards of organisation, excellence, and professional engagement.",
