    "mice.service4.description": "Strategic, high-impact platforms for the global pharmaceutical industry. Gervae facilitates meaningful connections between leading laboratories, industry innovators, and international buyers — creating the ideal environment for product launches, strategic partnerships, and industry leadership.",
    "mice.service5.title": "Tourism Exhibitions",
    "mice.service5.description": "Dynamic international trade shows that bring together the world's finest luxury travel brands, destination specialists, and hospitality professionals. Gervae curates compelling, well-orchestrated events that inspire connections and showcase excellence within the global travel community.",
