    "medical.page.content.patients.title": "Medical Treatment Visa",
    "medical.page.content.patients.description": "Gervae's Medical Visa concierge orchestrates world-class healthcare pursuits abroad. From specialist hospital selection and appointment coordination to travel logistics and accommodation arrangements, every element of the medical journey is managed with meticulous expertise, professionalism, and absolute discretion — enabling patients to focus exclusively on their healthcare outcomes.",
    "medical.page.content.doctors.title": "Business Visa",
    "medical.page.content.doctors.description": "For executives, entrepreneurs, and business professionals pursuing international opportunities — from strategic partnerships and market expansion to investment collaborations and global business operations — Gervae provides expert Business Visa support tailored to your specific professional requirements. We manage complete documentation preparation, regulatory compliance, and expedited processing, ensuring your visa application reflects the professional calibre of your international engagement. Travel arrangements, accommodation, and itinerary coordination are orchestrated seamlessly, allowing business professionals to focus entirely on their strategic objectives and professional growth.",
