    "medical.page.content.wellness.description": "Gervae offers comprehensive wellness tourism support for professionals and individuals seeking health restoration, therapeutic retreats, and wellness programmes abroad. Our carefully curated experiences connect clients with premier medical spas, accredited rehabilitation centres, and exclusive wellness destinations — each chosen for clinical excellence, proven therapeutic outcomes, and uncompromising luxury. From visa facilitation to travel logistics and accommodation, we manage everything seamlessly so guests can focus entirely on their wellness and recovery.",
    "medical.page.tab.family": "Family Visit Visa",
    "medical.page.content.family.title": "Family Visit Visa",
    "medical.page.content.family.description": "Gervae specialises in facilitating Family Visit Visas for Schengen countries, offering comprehensive support for individuals seeking to reunite with family members or close friends living in Europe. From gathering and verifying essential documents — such as formal invitation letters, proof of relationship, financial statements, and comprehensive travel insurance — to full application preparation and submission, we manage every step with meticulous care and professionalism. Our expertise ensures compliance with Schengen regulations while highlighting your strong ties to your home country. Beyond the visa process, Gervae provides personalised travel arrangements, including flights, ground transportation, and convenient accommodation, so you can concentrate fully on cherishing your time with loved ones.",
